{"tid":2375417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國持續擴建西沙南沙島礁　還在永暑礁設軍營超市","createTime":"2021-01-22T04:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:03:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f410648d82eae0fa0df1bf4fc5c577f11b70f4e","tid":2375417,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"中國在南海動作不斷，除演習外，中共亦持續擴建西沙及南沙島礁。中國央視軍事微博昨天（21日）報導，中共解放軍已在永暑礁設立軍營超市，供解放軍官兵購買，共有5大類約400種商品。<br />\n<br />\n中國央視軍事微博昨天（21日）晚間指出，中共解放軍在南沙島礁設立了軍營超市，已開放使用，包含生活用品、文具及體育用品等5大類，共有400多種商品，除了能讓解放軍人員在島上喝冷飲外，還稱能以優惠價賣給官兵，支援「掃碼支付」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3418742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3418742&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TTHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=8b0a2256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3418742&h=097a1fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3418742</a>"},{"pid":"a4684d3d179dba6fb3c54ff9288f795c90cef2fd","tid":2375417,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"歡迎登登光臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7414622f64661e67826c4aea488baca32f67b550","tid":2375417,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"咁都有得打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}